            <title>联想 ThinkBook 14+ 2025 款笔记本官宣，搭载酷睿 7 250H 处理器</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/821/635.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/821/635.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 06:46:03 GMT</updated>
                
                
            <content:encoded>
                <![CDATA[
                    
